  A real metadata file is obtained from:
    Google Admin Console → Apps → Web and mobile apps → <your app>
    → SAML attribute mapping → "Download Metadata"

  Key fields used by GoogleMetadataParser:
    - md:EntityDescriptor[@entityID]
        → https://accounts.google.com/o/saml2?idpid=<idpid>
    - md:IDPSSODescriptor/md:SingleSignOnService[@Binding=HTTP-POST][@Location]
        → https://accounts.google.com/o/saml2/idp?idpid=<idpid>
    - ds:X509Certificate
